# Smart Lender – Project Demonstration

**Demo Video:**
https://drive.google.com/file/d/11dCTX4SxPh0qRm-s40hptdVy0CCOpUzj/view?usp=drivesdk

**GitHub Repository:**
https://github.com/bavyagolla-lab/Smart-lender

**How to Run:**
1. Clone the repository.
2. Open the project folder.
3. Double-click `index.html` or open it using Live Server in VS Code.
4. The Smart Lender application will open in your browser.
